title: Nancy Guthrie missing case turns tense as YouTube streamers crowd her home and Jimmy Williams clashes with neighbor
summary_full: Nancy Guthrie has been missing since February 1, 2026, and the FBI and local police are still searching. YouTube streamers have crowded outside her home, live streaming updates and sparking speculation. Sheriff Chris Nanos defended the family after online claims. Authorities have received thousands of tips. No arrests have been made yet.
